  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd. \u0ba8\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd. \u0baa\u0bc0\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd 27 \u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Jaffna. Navali Sen. 27th Anniversary of Air Attack on Peter's Church",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna, Navali Sen. The 27th anniversary of the air attack on St. Peter's Church was held on Saturday evening, 09 September. A memorial service was held at Peter's Church.",
        "Following this, relatives of the deceased and members of the public paid their respects by lighting floral obelisks.",
        "On July 9, 1995, Navali Sen. 147 people were killed when three Air Force planes dropped 13 bombs in a row on displaced people who were staying at Peter's Church and Navali Sri Kathirgama Murugan Temple.",
        "Early that morning, the military carried out a military operation of advancing towards Valigamam areas with the help of missile attacks and airstrikes.",
        "Due to continuous shelling, the people who were displaced from their habitations towards Navali went to Navali and took shelter in Peter's Church and Navali Sri Kathirgama Murugan Temple.",
        "That morning, three planes suddenly arrived and dropped 13 bombs in a row on the church and temple where people were sheltering. In this bombing incident, 147 people, including children and women, were killed on the spot. More than 350 people were injured."
      ],
